   Started but OOM'd. Smaller scope this time — one viz at a time.

**6. End-to-end music generation pipeline** — Combine counterpoint-engine + groove-analyzer + spline-midi-smooth into a single pipeline: input a cantus firmus → generate counterpoint → apply groove → smooth velocity → output MIDI. This is the "prove it all works together" demo.

### LOWER PRIORITY / CREATIVE

**7. Build a MIDI-to-constraint translator** — Given any MIDI file, extract:
